name: Labkid6
summary: This game is available in Korean language only.  Labkid6 is an educational VR game that allows users to experience future careers through immersive virtual environments. Players explore various job roles, interact with realistic work scenarios, and learn about skills required for different professions in an engaging and hands-on way. Labkid6 is designed to help students and learners gain early insights into future career paths.
